---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import aboutImage from "../assets/images/about.webp";
---
<section id="about" class="min-h-screen px-6 py-24 lg:px-20 2xl:px-30 flex items-center">
    <article class="mx-auto w-full max-w-7xl grid grid-cols-1 xl:grid-cols-2 gap-10 xl:gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="max-w-2xl">
            <h1 class="font-playfair section-title font-semibold text-white text-3xl sm:text-4xl mb-6">
                ABOUT US
            </h1>

            <p class="text-[#8F8F8F] leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-base">
                BeardCut started as a dedicated corner for people who see personal care as a ritual. Our team combines classic techniques with modern styles so every client leaves with a look that truly matches their identity. We believe in precision, experience and comfort, so every visit is designed to feel like your own moment away from noise and distractions.
                <br><br>
                At BeardCut, we focus on more than haircuts. We create an authentic and close experience, with a relaxed environment and attentive service in every step.
            </p>
        </div>

        <Image
            src={aboutImage}
            alt="BeardCut barber performing a haircut in Austin, Texas"
            widths={[320, 420, 520, 640, 728]}
            sizes="(max-width: 768px) 92vw, (max-width: 1280px) 50vw, 640px"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
            fetchpriority="low"
            format="avif"
            quality={45}
            style="filter: saturate(0);"
            class="w-full max-w-2xl xl:ml-auto rounded-sm shadow-xl opacity-75 object-cover h-80 sm:h-105 lg:h-130"
        />
    </article>
</section>

